'''黏着小帶'''（Adherens junction/zonula adherens），亦稱「'''中間連接'''」（intermediate junction），係一種[[上皮細胞|上皮細胞]]之間的連接結構<ref>{{cite journal|last=Guo|first=Renyong|author2=Sakamoto, Hiroshi; Sugiura, Shigeki|title=Endothelial Cell Motility Is Compatible With Junctional Integrity|journal=Journal of Cellular Physiology|date=October 2006|doi=10.1002/jcp.20937|volume=211|pages=327–335}}</ref><ref name=He_Li>{{cite book|title=《組織學與胚胎學》|publisher=人民衛生出版社|ISBN=978-7-117-20646-4|edition=第三版|author=李和、李繼承等|pages=29|year=2015}}</ref>。

==結構==
該結構多位於閉鎖小帶下方，環繞上皮細胞頂部。該結構中間有15-20納米寬的縫隙。一種叫[[钙粘蛋白|钙粘蛋白]]的跨膜細胞黏附蛋白質爲該結構的核心。钙粘蛋白的細胞內部分與[[微絲|微絲]]相連，形成[[終末網|終末網]]（terminal web）結構<ref>{{cite journal | author = Yamada S, Pokutta S, Drees F, Weis W, Nelson W | title = Deconstructing the cadherin-catenin-actin complex. |journal = Cell | volume = 123 | issue = 5 | pages = 889–901 | year = 2005 | pmid = 16325582 | doi = 10.1016/j.cell.2005.09.020 | pmc=3368712}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author = Drees F, Pokutta S, Yamada S, Nelson W, Weis W | title = Alpha-catenin is a molecular switch that binds E-cadherin-beta-catenin and regulates actin-filament assembly. | journal = Cell | volume = 123 |issue = 5 | pages = 903–15 | year = 2005 | pmid = 16325583 | doi = 10.1016/j.cell.2005.09.021 | pmc=3369825}}</ref><ref name=He_Li/>。

==功能==
黏着小帶主要發揮黏着作用。另外，此結構亦能維持微纖毛和細胞的形態。該結構還能起到傳遞細胞收縮張力的作用<ref name=He_Li/>。

